{"tid":438090,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新手求教 大家去大阪住酒店定民宿","createTime":"2017-10-16T14:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T12:28:33.000Z","uid":7879,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"321f833154d027b4180f9a9b422078d6ca5b34af","tid":438090,"uid":7879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"大家去大阪住酒店定民宿如果住酒店的話住邊一間？"},{"pid":"5a38eabe24eb200de404df44890e5f4175272b81","tid":438090,"uid":5218,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"咁既問題都問得出你不如訓街啦。"},{"pid":"2763186f1c67c4bda709b7f370fbda717de82ec2","tid":438090,"uid":133375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"大阪梗係住酒店<br />\n民宿唔靚同埋唔就腳<br />\n又要等屋主開門，未必間間有得擺定行李先<br />\n酒店住難波/心齋橋附近最好"},{"pid":"05097db3f9384e41f7d12f7e40c78a560693738c","tid":438090,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"幾多個人去先？"},{"pid":"eb227f9226d6033bf4b7eda455a80cac64f160e8","tid":438090,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"商務酒店好多百零蚊一晚<br />\n安心又安全<br />\nCheck out有得擺行李<br />\n民宿好麻煩"},{"pid":"f4ce02a24099a8a4121cca4cb3d332ea69b72be7","tid":438090,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>商務酒店好多百零蚊一晚<br />\n安心又安全<br />\nCheck out有得擺行李<br />\n民宿好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多年前百幾蚊晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecbb5758088990118a824e78f2d82c945f2f9b7","tid":438090,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>商務酒店好多百零蚊一晚<br />\n安心又安全<br />\nCheck out有得擺行李<br />\n民宿好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多年前百幾蚊晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 深圳啲垃圾房都要200啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73b1281ae747ec2898d0f574b8a62c5f076d6aa","tid":438090,"uid":44814,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁既問題都問得出你不如訓街啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實巴打唔洗咁串<br />\n你搵到錢鍾意住高級旅館 溫泉旅館係你嘅事<br />\n可能人地學生 啱啱出黎做野 成村人去 好多唔同case<br />\n何必以己度人"},{"pid":"95894f116e186119fe7adb309a60d2c18a71cafb","tid":438090,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"其實酒店好平<br />\n<br />\n唔係話5星級果D<br />\n<br />\n只係普通3星級住得下人<br />\n<br />\n都係幾百蚊1晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ab517b7b88b8d56e5be0cc888340f2979c43e9","tid":438090,"uid":7229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"多人/住得耐（幾日）/想冇咁死板- airbnb<br />\n住一兩日/方便 - 酒店<br />\n酒店有得擺行李係方便好多，日本最大size locker 700~800 yen 一日<br />\n同埋酒店實有拖鞋牙刷牙膏etc 唔洗煩，最正係有浴衣帶少件訓覺衫，同埋實有電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d1a95f10a68d969ef78c903ccc2f36eefe8533","tid":438090,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>商務酒店好多百零蚊一晚<br />\n安心又安全<br />\nCheck out有得擺行李<br />\n民宿好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多年前百幾蚊晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 深圳啲垃圾房都要200啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天王寺 新今宮<br />\n好多平酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭兩個站到遊客區"},{"pid":"1c991a0ac49ea0ffeee13c35fc85ea6a068b27ca","tid":438090,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>商務酒店好多百零蚊一晚<br />\n安心又安全<br />\nCheck out有得擺行李<br />\n民宿好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多年前百幾蚊晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 深圳啲垃圾房都